Class Estimator<Y>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umn.cs.spatialHadoop.Estimator<Y>

  • public class Estimator<Y>
extends Object
    Estimates a given value by taking a random sample from sample space until the confidence interval of the calculated value is acceptable
    Author:
    Ahmed Eldawy

    • Field Detail

      • alpha

        protected double alpha
        A value from [0, 1] to determine how large is the confidence interval needed. A value closer to zero gives a narrow interval. For example, setting this value to 0.05 returns a 95% confidence interval.
